  <title>Xz-&xz-version;</title>

  <indexterm zone="ch-system-xz">
    <primary sortas="a-xz">Xz</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title/>

    <para>Xz 包包含用于压缩和解压文件的程序。它提供了对 lzma 和较新的 xz 压缩格式的功能。使用 <command>xz</command> 压缩文本文件能够产生比使用传统的 <command>gzip</command> 或 <command>bzip2</command> 命令更好的压缩率。</para>

    <segmentedlist>
      <segtitle>&buildtime;</segtitle>
      <segtitle>&diskspace;</segtitle>

      <seglistitem>
        <seg>&xz-ch6-sbu;</seg>
        <seg>&xz-ch6-du;</seg>
      </seglistitem>
    </segmentedlist>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Xz 的安装</title>

    <para>准备 Xz 进行编译:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="configure">./configure --prefix=/usr --docdir=/usr/share/doc/xz-&xz-version;</userinput></screen>

    <para>编译包:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="make">make</userinput></screen>

    <para>要测试结果，执行:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="test">make check</userinput></screen>

  <para>安装包:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

